  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About game</strong></h2>Farmageddon is a tower defense strategy game based on a post-apocalyptic story. Defeat hordes of infected, earn money by farming crops, buy upgrades at the proper time, and compete with others on world leaderboards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Situation</strong></h2>Why farm? Why deal with the infected? Why you? Well... Humanity developed a special protein to protect crops, but our research turned against us in a horrible way. Now, it's up to you, a farmers who grows their own crops, to save humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><br>🔸 Horror-themed story<br>🔸 Gameplay consequences of your strategic actions<br>🔸 Ability to choose the difficulty level<br>🔸 Global leaderboards<br>🔸 Rewarding feeling after overcoming a wave<br>🔸 Graphical satisfaction<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farming</strong></h2>Spend money to buy crops and earn even more money!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/8b1c375bfa83d6eb33689c7dcefd3091.poster.avif?t=1723824083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/8b1c375bfa83d6eb33689c7dcefd3091.webm?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/8b1c375bfa83d6eb33689c7dcefd3091.mp4?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Class</strong></h2>Many different classes of infected. Beat them all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/47ce0c930803ea39d38b211c133f642e.poster.avif?t=1723824083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/47ce0c930803ea39d38b211c133f642e.webm?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/47ce0c930803ea39d38b211c133f642e.mp4?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Physics</strong></h2>Just imagine going through hordes of bodies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/5214b2ef61583addeb5fe4e92df9d46d.poster.avif?t=1723824083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/5214b2ef61583addeb5fe4e92df9d46d.webm?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/5214b2ef61583addeb5fe4e92df9d46d.mp4?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About game</strong></h2>Farmageddon is a tower defense strategy game based on a post-apocalyptic story. Defeat hordes of infected, earn money by farming crops, buy upgrades at the proper time, and compete with others on world leaderboards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Situation</strong></h2>Why farm? Why deal with the infected? Why you? Well... Humanity developed a special protein to protect crops, but our research turned against us in a horrible way. Now, it's up to you, a farmers who grows their own crops, to save humanity.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key features</strong></h2><br>🔸 Horror-themed story<br>🔸 Gameplay consequences of your strategic actions<br>🔸 Ability to choose the difficulty level<br>🔸 Global leaderboards<br>🔸 Rewarding feeling after overcoming a wave<br>🔸 Graphical satisfaction<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farming</strong></h2>Spend money to buy crops and earn even more money!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/8b1c375bfa83d6eb33689c7dcefd3091.poster.avif?t=1723824083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/8b1c375bfa83d6eb33689c7dcefd3091.webm?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/8b1c375bfa83d6eb33689c7dcefd3091.mp4?t=1723824083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Class</strong></h2>Many different classes of infected. Beat them all!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991590/extras/47ce0c930803ea39d38b211c133f642e.poster.avif?t=1723824083\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c